      <h2 id="special-thoughts-on-healing-after-losing-a-pet">Special Thoughts on Healing After Losing a Pet</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>Healing from pet loss takes time.  These messages offer encouragement and hope for the future, while acknowledging the pain of the present.</p>
<p>Allow yourself time to grieve.  Remember, there is no right or wrong way to feel.  Surround yourself with loved ones, and cherish the memories of your special companion.  Their love lives on in your heart.  The pain will lessen with time, but the love will remain forever.  May the warmth of memories bring you comfort, and may peace eventually find its way to your heart.</p>
    
  
